lg.l:
As I have announced the true theory

of the youth, manhood, womanhood,

of These States, I adhere to it;

To young men my problems offering—

no dallier I—I the muscle of

their brains trying;

I love you—but I launch myself

from you and from all that live, 
   —I depart from materials,

I love you—but I launch myself off

from you, 
   and henceforth
    from all that live,

Somebody's breath falls around me like dew— around
me—Somebody's pulse beats the
tympans of my ears;
